EN: The fragrance of fresh flowers hit me in the face, filling the entire room with scent.

ZH: 油烟扑面而来，让人感到不适。
EN: The smell of grease hit me in the face, making me uncomfortable.

ZH: 雪花扑面而来，白茫茫的一片。
EN: The snowflakes hit me in the face, covering everything in white.

